Package: libgif
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: provides API functions for reading and writing GIF files
 GIFLIB provides API functions for reading and writing GIF files.
 .
 This package provides the shared library libgif.

Package: libgif-bin
