 This package provides tools for reading writing, and converting GIF
 files.

Package: libgif-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Provides: giflib-dev
Depends: libgif (= ${binary:Version}), libz-dev
Description: Development headers and GIFLIB static library
 This package provides libgif.a, headers and pkgconfig data required
 to build applications, libraries or plugins using the GIFLIB API.
